    "question_id" : 1092219,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>If you add in Hamcrest and JUnit4, you could do:</p>\n<pre><code>String x = &quot;foo bar&quot;;\nAssert.assertThat(x, CoreMatchers.containsString(&quot;foo&quot;));\n</code></pre>\n<p>With some static imports, it looks a lot better:</p>\n<pre><code>assertThat(x, containsString(&quot;foo&quot;));\n</code></pre>\n<p>The static imports needed would be:</p>\n<pre><code>import static org.hamcrest.MatcherAssert.assertThat;\nimport static org.hamcrest.CoreMatchers.containsString;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
