    "body" : "<p>It's too late, but just to update I got it done with below syntax</p>\n\n<pre><code>import org.hamcrest.core.StringContains;\nimport org.junit.Assert;\n\nAssert.assertThat(\"this contains test\", StringContains.containsString(\"test\"));\n</code></pre>\n"
