    "question_id" : 1092219,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I wrote this utility method</p>\n<pre><code>public static void assertContains(String string, String subString) {\n    Assertions.assertTrue(string.contains(subString));\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
